{"tid":1416462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]大家都話入機場 究竟入到去我哋可以做咩","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:41:23.000Z","uid":109127,"like":59,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"da1bdeb9fda9b0743612f58af3293c897ed6f1d2","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"愈嚟愈多人討論去機場集會，小弟有小小見解，大家係和理飛下究竟可以做啲咩，不妨大家一齊討論去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要圍接機大堂</span></span>，等抵港旅客走唔倒，倒塞入去羅行李/入境櫃位，最終塞到去登機閘口，啲人落唔倒機，更加唔洗諗上下一批客。啲機塞係泊位走唔倒，自然就冇飛機可以降落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 所以唔需要塞離境大堂，就算俾你搞到一個人都上唔倒機大不了吉機飛走，影響唔倒機場運作，仲會搞到要搭飛機嘅人同示威者爭執/衝突。<br />\n<br />\n3. 係果度無需要嗌口號，甚至無需要特登著黑衫，亦都唔洗帶口罩。好似平時咁出街打扮再拖兩個(吉)gip ，大家都只係泥接朋友機。狗泥到都唔知捉邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 接機大堂有冷氣有電源有wifi有廁所有餐廳，舒舒服服，被塞嘅抵港旅客都一樣。對所有人影響最少，成本最低，但就可以令機場癱瘓<br />\n<br />\n5. 每個鐘有咁多班機降落，瘋狂有人抵埗，但又走唔倒，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等於源源不絕有人幫手堵塞，</span></span>唔洗十個八個鐘成個機場應該可以gg<br />\n<br />\n6. 搵個週未大家當郊遊去機場嘆氣用免費wifi，輕鬆抗爭，夠人嘅話朝早開始塞分分鐘未入夜機場已玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cb32de8f0de6024fa6b3396e8a00536123471e","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f464e569def56cebbe62880f025978b6871d14ed","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:12:17.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"76dcb04b592e8a2ff95fdc93461aa76f44604db6","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:12:32.000Z","msg":"十連無難道"},{"pid":"55d27b63e461b0e94652c6142d44d57d4b1d0d5e","tid":1416462,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:12:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7702e0a1cfd4678ea77d78ef6f1bbe067d65c289","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"推到更多人討論"},{"pid":"511f31ac6024bca09c896cb1da5db3b77ef61c10","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:16:47.000Z","msg":"繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b8bc43e765122019504da1088595ef3158f098","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"fdab8840f645fadcc323513de22001600202c525","tid":1416462,"uid":298116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:17:41.000Z","msg":"可以周圍airdrop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fee1f1e05ebcc8066cd4067fff0f4d24f06104b","tid":1416462,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:17:57.000Z","msg":"和理非請你永遠記住<br />\n&quot;不割蓆&quot;唔係叫你要認同哂所有抗爭手段，你絕對可以隨時提出意見；<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">&quot;不割蓆&quot; 意思係叫你就算點都好，都唔好離隊！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;絕不放棄，抗爭到底，直到勝利&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n[ 溫故知新！] 成日話&quot;不割蓆&quot;, 都想大家深入明白咩叫&quot;不割蓆&quot;先！！(利申：不割)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415759</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8020686cd2641fc878b3160cfcad858e73e365e3","tid":1416462,"uid":125179,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:19:28.000Z","msg":"唔需要堵塞，機場留返做文宣，支持更大民意（不同國家既旅客/轉機既人）<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好搞到佢地<br />\n<br />\n有禮地用文宣去話俾全世界聽香港發生緊咩事！"},{"pid":"241f77481b1a4a68a03687ed4b33372b1f9e7ed6","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fdab8840f645fadcc323513de22001600202c525","tid":1416462,"uid":298116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:17:41.000Z","msg":"可以周圍airdrop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:19:57.000Z","msg":"Airdrop比遊客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f8ecf928a24ee0da3d1291f41f44927206beb5","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:22:13.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"2f3b68c5402259ba481003c85050807862897cc5","tid":1416462,"uid":206079,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"機場勇武真係要諗諗<br />\n又有機場特警 又有入無出<br />\n如果一個唔覺意殃及池魚 誤中遊客<br />\n有機會令外媒唔企我地呢面"},{"pid":"95ef63be78225f4603ec90280bd3620aba801a67","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"2f3b68c5402259ba481003c85050807862897cc5","tid":1416462,"uid":206079,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"機場勇武真係要諗諗<br />\n又有機場特警 又有入無出<br />\n如果一個唔覺意殃及池魚 誤中遊客<br />\n有機會令外媒唔企我地呢面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"所以無諗過勇武 純接機<br />\n好似平時啲妹妹仔接偶像機塞爆機場咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋無著黑衫無叫口號 最多都係默默地send airdrop做文宣<br />\n咁班狗要捉都唔知邊啲係真接機"},{"pid":"04fa3477fc32fc39fda884b2d0a30de3e368c42b","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"510ba0f121b6a2cc5d735acadc1d4471f7fdf1c0","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8020686cd2641fc878b3160cfcad858e73e365e3","tid":1416462,"uid":125179,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:19:28.000Z","msg":"唔需要堵塞，機場留返做文宣，支持更大民意（不同國家既旅客/轉機既人）<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好搞到佢地<br />\n<br />\n有禮地用文宣去話俾全世界聽香港發生緊咩事！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:57:03.000Z","msg":"只係搵一日大家拖住兩個gip去接機，又唔係一齊著黑衫，一齊嗌口號，只係太多人塞住晒，無任何衝擊，亦唔會對遊客有咩不禮貌對待<br />\n文宣可以同時做，塞住晒嘅時候如果身邊有旅客，悶悶地當然就係傾下計，等佢地了解下，同時又可以幫自己練下英文<br />\n明白咁樣對遊客一定會帶嚟不便，但機場作為香港其中一個重要經濟命脈，純粹一個普通集會咁去做文宣，影響力有限。<br />\n呢兩個月外國媒體都報導咗好多香港嘅嘢，但外國媒幫我地又點，佢唔會令政府跪低，我地最終靠最主要嘅都係自己"},{"pid":"28b5b1865aeaf0ffcf99bb62839d6851e3a97a01","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"再推到更多人一齊討論"},{"pid":"b866c3ead42cd0a648d36c6ebbe3813f720ce176","tid":1416462,"uid":221437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"673192066c406467e9861667dd960704c89f8fd1","tid":1416462,"uid":221437,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"如果多人佔跑道，我諗可行)?<br />\n佢唔會開槍射晒我哋咁多個掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但前提真係要多人<br />\n否則太少人實俾人射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43abf612ac9a9492bafadaa4625d6096553d55af","tid":1416462,"uid":296109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:13:36.000Z","msg":"推，東涌撚表示 完全冇問題。"},{"pid":"0b46fbf1eecb831b59c595ad522dca4657d8402a","tid":1416462,"uid":286677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:18:50.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"87fb15877a034b75068ce07da0afa1d9c71aa144","tid":1416462,"uid":247180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"673192066c406467e9861667dd960704c89f8fd1","tid":1416462,"uid":221437,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"如果多人佔跑道，我諗可行)?<br />\n佢唔會開槍射晒我哋咁多個掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但前提真係要多人<br />\n否則太少人實俾人射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:20:09.000Z","msg":"咁容易俾你入禁區咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a89bba934c2ce8bf5384643aee4990b74bcc81","tid":1416462,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:20:32.000Z","msg":"重組警隊 獨立調查<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n堅守香港 保衛家園<br />\n<br />\n[公投] 口號唔止得一個嘅！比多幾個啦！重組警隊 獨立調查<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416741</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3cc09570105d713620f568141277731e65355297","tid":1416462,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:21:26.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"c3e2265bc9c0e4df9928511f587e04a96e0a07c8","tid":1416462,"uid":251866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:22:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ee306e2ad7b577690ff38e331953ea046bdbcbe","tid":1416462,"uid":61611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:22:24.000Z","msg":"泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0552536d6a8f48365491a0b939627a509a2e52be","tid":1416462,"uid":200026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:23:17.000Z","msg":"光復香港, 時代革命!"},{"pid":"4b10af8714f28c293791fe03d318b60946af58e1","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ee306e2ad7b577690ff38e331953ea046bdbcbe","tid":1416462,"uid":61611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:22:24.000Z","msg":"泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:23:53.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罰抄十次<br />\n嚟嚟嚟嚟嚟嚟嚟嚟嚟嚟"},{"pid":"2b2d1f2e97a2bd17751cc2e94e1989b9d85cd96e","tid":1416462,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:24:39.000Z","msg":"我覺得可以做多啲文宣同分工<br />\n今日去咗 見到大家都好有heart分咗三個區叫口號同貼連龍場<br />\n另外 可以做多啲文宣<br />\n派傳單(唔同語言) 多啲同遊客交流 等佢地知道詳細係發生咩事 接機大堂A/B可以企多啲人"},{"pid":"6a2f9c41d19d355858575da0edd101df95a1f43d","tid":1416462,"uid":286423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:25:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔使曬唔曬淋雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d149e8cd2b326f5baa2bf8b8dd8473b0f34f621","tid":1416462,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:25:20.000Z","msg":"機場係文宣好機會呀!!"},{"pid":"1bcc4f5ba8b98402a404c0e6b2f3a32cae22ebc4","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"673192066c406467e9861667dd960704c89f8fd1","tid":1416462,"uid":221437,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"如果多人佔跑道，我諗可行)?<br />\n佢唔會開槍射晒我哋咁多個掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但前提真係要多人<br />\n否則太少人實俾人射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:26:05.000Z","msg":"難度太高 比人圍就跳落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97438f5ba7214bfb5b9a342a859ae0a1755842bc","tid":1416462,"uid":70695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da1bdeb9fda9b0743612f58af3293c897ed6f1d2","tid":1416462,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"愈嚟愈多人討論去機場集會，小弟有小小見解，大家係和理飛下究竟可以做啲咩，不妨大家一齊討論去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要圍接機大堂</span></span>，等抵港旅客走唔倒，倒塞入去羅行李/入境櫃位，最終塞到去登機閘口，啲人落唔倒機，更加唔洗諗上下一批客。啲機塞係泊位走唔倒，自然就冇飛機可以降落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 所以唔需要塞離境大堂，就算俾你搞到一個人都上唔倒機大不了吉機飛走，影響唔倒機場運作，仲會搞到要搭飛機嘅人同示威者爭執/衝突。<br />\n<br />\n3. 係果度無需要嗌口號，甚至無需要特登著黑衫，亦都唔洗帶口罩。好似平時咁出街打扮再拖兩個(吉)gip ，大家都只係泥接朋友機。狗泥到都唔知捉邊個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 接機大堂有冷氣有電源有wifi有廁所有餐廳，舒舒服服，被塞嘅抵港旅客都一樣。對所有人影響最少，成本最低，但就可以令機場癱瘓<br />\n<br />\n5. 每個鐘有咁多班機降落，瘋狂有人抵埗，但又走唔倒，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等於源源不絕有人幫手堵塞，</span></span>唔洗十個八個鐘成個機場應該可以gg<br />\n<br />\n6. 搵個週未大家當郊遊去機場嘆氣用免費wifi，輕鬆抗爭，夠人嘅話朝早開始塞分分鐘未入夜機場已玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280e1cf7e8bf7df68791eaafeba36d4a708eb062","tid":1416462,"uid":70695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2031006d08ab7606636e772214917290bad6198","tid":1416462,"uid":70695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"pish!"},{"pid":"676b0539e4f548a394a00fea09f9074a7f53a6ae","tid":1416462,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:29:27.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"54582e46d99e1061f1c260e160f67fa38fcde3af","tid":1416462,"uid":276527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:29:28.000Z","msg":"機場好大, 要倒塞返去登機閘口好似有d難. 同埋人不是車, 唔係咁易塞得死.<br />\n<br />\n塞機場幹道有無得諗?"},{"pid":"00759fb79e4942b00f16e6dcf29d57d2761c0c81","tid":1416462,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a00a3d2c6c32aeb2a1e4d27955f5e9d7a573cbb","tid":1416462,"uid":102321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco